snippet.title: PC-9801: Foxy English translation project - Proof of concept
snippet.description:
UPDATE: Finished and released! Download here: https://archive.org/details/foxy-en-1-0

While Yu-No is being proofred and corrected, I have started a project of smaller scale : bring the early classic strategy game by Elf, Foxy, in English language !
Here's the first mission with menus done. Obviously, it needs a bit of polishing, but here it goes.
